      • asTable

        @Pure
public static def asTable(descriptions : List<IssueDatabaseExtensions.IssueDescription>) : List<List<String>> 
        Description copied from class: IssueDatabaseExtensions
        Replies a table description for the list of issues.

        The result is a table with 3 columns:

        • Column 1: index of the issue
        • Column 2: the code of the issue
        • Column 3: the message and description of the issue
        • Column 4: the importance level of the issue
        Parameters:
        descriptions - the list of issue descriptions to render.
        sort - indicates if the table rows should be sorted on simples codes.
        Returns:
        the table content.
